These are derived from:
https://github.com/orblancog/elegant-mode for Emacs
https://github.com/orblancog/elegant-vim for VIM

I update the original copy with a script that results in a more 
complete list of highlightable elements and commands.

Installation instructions for Emacs:
  M+X package-install-file RETURN elegant/editors/emacs/elegant.el RETURN

Installation instructions for VIM:
  Copy the contents of elegant/editors/vim/vimrc to ~/.vimrc
  Copy elegant/editors/vim/after/plugin/elegant.vim to ~/.vim/after/plugin/elegant.vim
  Copy elegant/editors/vim/autoload/elegantcomplete.vim to ~/.vim/autoload/elegantcomplete.vim
  Copy elegant/editors/vim/ftdetect/elegant.vim to ~/.vim/ftdetect/elegant.vim
  Copy elegant/editors/vim/syntax/elegant.vim to ~/.vim/syntax/elegant.vim
